1126.name: CuAl9Fe
1126.Applications: Joint welds or building up of aluminum bronze. Cladding components undergoing metal to metal wear. Joining steel to copper alloys, cast iron and or bronze.
1126.Suitable_For: Suitable for seawater resistant applications. Joining steel to copper alloys, cast iron and or bronze. Excellent for metal spraying. Ship propellers, shipbuilding, pump building, shafts, guide grooves etc, UNS : C 60600 - C 61600 - C 68700, DIN : Cu Al5 - Cu Al8 - CuZn20Al2, Werkstoff Nr : 2.0916 - 2.0920 - 2.0960
